1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,650
Joe Salesman, Joe Executive, Joe Professional Worker, Josephine Housewife.

2
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:10,931
They all often try to build strength and get ready with office chats,

3
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:18,051
coffee breaks, sharpening pencils, reading, personal business, getting the desk cleared off, TV,

4
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:20,931
and dozens of other little escape devices.

5
00:00:21,841 --> 00:00:24,051
But there's a way to break this habit.

6
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:28,451
Tell yourself, I'm in condition right now to begin.

7
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:31,091
I can't gain a thing by putting it off.

8
00:00:31,361 --> 00:00:36,130
I'll use the get ready time and energy to get going instead.

9
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:46,451
What we want more than anything else in our business, an executive in a machine tool company said in an address to a group of sales executives,

10
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:51,011
is more people who get sound ideas and then push them through.

11
00:00:51,361 --> 00:00:57,331
There's not one job in our production and marketing setup that can't be done better, a lot better.

12
00:00:57,520 --> 00:01:00,770
I don't want to infer that we're not doing a good job now.

13
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:01,571
We are.
